{"tid":365164,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［JJ插熔岩］求初心者哲學書推介","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T06:11:14.000Z","uid":66158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4123044f9cb506b54ce0100cd2c9fb68895aacc2","tid":365164,"uid":66158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"想接觸有關哲學方面嘅知識<br />\n但係就咁wiki一下都有好多門派好多topic咁<br />\n唔知可以係邊個位入手好<br />\n希望呢到有高手可以推介下有無咩書係啱初哥睇<br />\n盡量希望係中文 但如果你地推介本書係好高質 <br />\n英文都唔區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a4c719b6f913194d7a34052be1620dccf69601","tid":365164,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"我啱啱買左本哲學百科  你去書局應該見到  入面有大部份哲學家既介紹  都幾足夠初級入門"},{"pid":"4005fee91e1b7c71481b7fd3cad369ab5807a939","tid":365164,"uid":84622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"John Hosper -introduction to philosophical analysis 跟topic 咁寫既，寫得好清晰，好有英美哲學影子"},{"pid":"cceb98a8063a7bdea6eaa49f9bd32a0fb0a96173","tid":365164,"uid":113657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啱啱買左本哲學百科  你去書局應該見到  入面有大部份哲學家既介紹  都幾足夠初級入門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/124550_60be874232fc678fa260c0e0178377de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F124550_60be874232fc678fa260c0e0178377de.jpg&h=9b05600f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a91c40deb01a3589cde3fffbca70f5576bfb1a71","tid":365164,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>John Hosper -introduction to philosophical analysis 跟topic 咁寫既，寫得好清晰，好有英美哲學影子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有心睇完呢本野  都真係有d誠意"},{"pid":"7c8d1b20e0af54e9e64e97537e793844b19daa0d","tid":365164,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"反而我想知多啲哲學問題 之後自己念下再聽下其他人既睇法<br />\n感覺哲學係一門純思考既學科<br />\n需要既反而係一啲令人思考既問題"},{"pid":"bc0deb13b5f508c2ace16e8cd422292161104443","tid":365164,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"哲學概論 冀劍制<br />\nIntroduction to Philosophy. Peter K.Mclnerny<br />\n後者強烈推薦"},{"pid":"5badbd01142d5b567ff2fecd1330a3f00d39caec","tid":365164,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哲學概論 冀劍制<br />\nIntroduction to Philosophy. Peter K.Mclnerny<br />\n後者強烈推薦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後者有中文"},{"pid":"b6f0f8c7c34469691968876ca71dfe51b1694f4d","tid":365164,"uid":137600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"蘇菲的世界"},{"pid":"f8a59ca41952411a90a7d068f77dc66edc6d2fab","tid":365164,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而我想知多啲哲學問題 之後自己念下再聽下其他人既睇法<br />\n感覺哲學係一門純思考既學科<br />\n需要既反而係一啲令人思考既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住哲學問題來讀係ok, <br />\n睇下d人點去分析解答 幫到你點去考慮有咩可能性，點樣嘅答案係有希望辯護到<br />\n其他人嘅答案又有點樣嘅問題，優劣之處<br />\n其他人又會點樣回應其他人或者你嘅答案<br />\n<br />\n呢d野憑空靠自己係思考唔出<br />\n好多人單係睇個哲學問題，憑空自己答，就反而扯到好遠"},{"pid":"d17918c70cf0c1bd994ceb3693e9ba52e31d3407","tid":365164,"uid":135368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:18:38.000Z","msg":"哲學major表示睇 正義：一場思辨之旅<br />\n入門程度"},{"pid":"05ca38994e109fcb71c6a305e401f3df1f159353","tid":365164,"uid":135068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T20:22:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7aeeba4763f154227ad58a475796e907f4b27396","tid":365164,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T22:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哲學major表示睇 正義：一場思辨之旅<br />\n入門程度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> major<br />\n我當年都好想讀<br />\n無咁大勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98a3e471e6eb93a2b8f279052604cd0738f541e","tid":365164,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而我想知多啲哲學問題 之後自己念下再聽下其他人既睇法<br />\n感覺哲學係一門純思考既學科<br />\n需要既反而係一啲令人思考既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住哲學問題來讀係ok, <br />\n睇下d人點去分析解答 幫到你點去考慮有咩可能性，點樣嘅答案係有希望辯護到<br />\n其他人嘅答案又有點樣嘅問題，優劣之處<br />\n其他人又會點樣回應其他人或者你嘅答案<br />\n<br />\n呢d野憑空靠自己係思考唔出<br />\n好多人單係睇個哲學問題，憑空自己答，就反而扯到好遠</blockquote><br />\n有冇咩呢類既好書/好問題推一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邏輯學 我都好有興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a464e380915363416068bed4a6a8204089962b","tid":365164,"uid":135368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哲學major表示睇 正義：一場思辨之旅<br />\n入門程度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> major<br />\n我當年都好想讀<br />\n無咁大勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ed26aa0d635af77ecae8f9a1b7c3a71b712fbd","tid":365164,"uid":135368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而我想知多啲哲學問題 之後自己念下再聽下其他人既睇法<br />\n感覺哲學係一門純思考既學科<br />\n需要既反而係一啲令人思考既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住哲學問題來讀係ok, <br />\n睇下d人點去分析解答 幫到你點去考慮有咩可能性，點樣嘅答案係有希望辯護到<br />\n其他人嘅答案又有點樣嘅問題，優劣之處<br />\n其他人又會點樣回應其他人或者你嘅答案<br />\n<br />\n呢d野憑空靠自己係思考唔出<br />\n好多人單係睇個哲學問題，憑空自己答，就反而扯到好遠</blockquote><br />\n有冇咩呢類既好書/好問題推一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邏輯學 我都好有興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個本好出名"},{"pid":"42f1f70fa6dae555a1f79d4b0592856d8533e196","tid":365164,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而我想知多啲哲學問題 之後自己念下再聽下其他人既睇法<br />\n感覺哲學係一門純思考既學科<br />\n需要既反而係一啲令人思考既問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住哲學問題來讀係ok, <br />\n睇下d人點去分析解答 幫到你點去考慮有咩可能性，點樣嘅答案係有希望辯護到<br />\n其他人嘅答案又有點樣嘅問題，優劣之處<br />\n其他人又會點樣回應其他人或者你嘅答案<br />\n<br />\n呢d野憑空靠自己係思考唔出<br />\n好多人單係睇個哲學問題，憑空自己答，就反而扯到好遠</blockquote><br />\n有冇咩呢類既好書/好問題推一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邏輯學 我都好有興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇呢本啦 邏輯學  <br />\n<a href=\"http://en.bookfi.net/book/1100797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.bookfi.net%2Fbook%2F1100797&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqETPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d3571ee1\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.bookfi.net/book/1100797</a><br />\n唔係正式教邏輯 （如果正式學，係需要做練習，好似學數學咁） <br />\n但本書連結到 邏輯學同其他哲學問題嘅關係<br />\n<br />\n到你睇完覺得有趣 先再正式學邏輯 都可以嘅"},{"pid":"c50c7ad413807eeb7e1e1bd17bf2a20a723adeed","tid":365164,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}